      "writtenOn": "2016-08-09T23:47:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If you make this a std::unique_ptr\u003cCommandWaitInfo\u003e, then you don\u0027t have to do the delete *elt on line 71.\n\nIn fact, since erase erases the element \"if it exists\", you wouldn\u0027t even need to do the find.",
