      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-08-09T23:47:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Personally, I\u0027d prefer that you make a block just before you declare the AutoLock, and terminate it here, so that the destructor does the unlock.  This (to me) emphasizes the duration of the lock.  I think this is worth having to declare \"res\" outside this block.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 147,
