      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-08-09T23:47:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "These hostcmd_handles are used only for sendCommandAndGetResult, right?  Perhaps there should be a version of sendCommand that doesn\u0027t take this argument, and just passes some constant to hostSignal?  (Here and just below.)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 166,
