        "id": 1099352
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-08-09T23:47:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I would not refer to the timeline_id as part of the timeline state.  (Since the only way to name a timeline is via a timeline_id, there\u0027s no need to query it -- so it\u0027s not really part of the state.)  So just say it\u0027s has a value, and that timelines are named by uint64_t identifiers, unique across the virtual device.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 81,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 82,
        "endChar": 26
      },
      "revId": "cfba63e2a3244bbebcbb650faa8174c0b62a09e9",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": false
